Lionel Messi: &quot;All year I've been telling the club and the president that I want to go out, and I thought it was time now.&quot;<br />
<br />
Lionel Messi: &quot;The truth is that there's been no project [at Barcelona] and nothing in a while - they juggle and they're plugging holes as things go by. As I said before, I always thought about the well-being of my family and the club.&quot;
